========,1,preface.
Bay View is a village in Erie County, Ohio, United States.
The population was 632 at the 2010 census.
It is part of the Sandusky, Ohio Metropolitan Statistical Area.
The village consists primarily of summer homes (many converted to year-round use) and a few small businesses.
The community has a scenic view of Sandusky Bay.
The village was incorporated in 1951.
